                         <literal> A>[] </literal>, <literal> A>=[] </literal>,
                         <literal> A&lt;[] </literal>, <literal> A&lt;=[] </literal>,
                         <literal> []>A </literal>, <literal> []>=A </literal>,
                         <literal> []&lt;A </literal> и <literal> []&lt;=A </literal> теперь возвращают
